#: src/components/pages/about/AboutHeader.tsx
msgid "This is an open-source test application — not a product or a company. Its sole purpose is to provide a realistic, multi-page React app where different i18n libraries can be integrated and measured under identical conditions."
msgstr "This is an open-source test application — not a product or a company. Its sole purpose is to provide a realistic, multi-page React app where different i18n libraries can be integrated and measured under identical conditions."

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "Bundle size impact"
msgstr "包大小影响"

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "The additional JavaScript bytes sent to users when the i18n library and its translation files are included. This directly affects download time on slow networks."
msgstr "The additional JavaScript bytes sent to users when the i18n library and its translation files are included. This directly affects download time on slow networks."

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "Rendering overhead"
msgstr "渲染开销"

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "How much extra time the library adds to React's render cycle. Libraries that inject translations via a single context provider can cause unnecessary re-renders across the component tree."
msgstr "How much extra time the library adds to React's render cycle. Libraries that inject translations via a single context provider can cause unnecessary re-renders across the component tree."

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "Hydration cost"
msgstr "注水成本"

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "During SSR, translation data is serialized into HTML. Large dictionaries increase the HTML payload and slow down hydration — the moment the page becomes interactive."
msgstr "During SSR, translation data is serialized into HTML. Large dictionaries increase the HTML payload and slow down hydration — the moment the page becomes interactive."

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "Lazy loading effectiveness"
msgstr "延迟加载有效性"

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "Whether splitting translations by route or namespace actually reduces the initial load, and what trade-offs it introduces (waterfall requests, FOUC, cache complexity)."
msgstr "按路线或命名空间拆分翻译是否真的能减少初始负载，以及它引入了哪些权衡（瀑布请求、FOUC、缓存复杂性）。"

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "Locale switch speed"
msgstr "本地语言切换速度"

#: src/components/pages/about/WhatWeMeasure.tsx
msgid "How fast the app can switch from one language to another at runtime — including fetching new translations, re-rendering components, and updating the DOM."
msgstr "应用程序在运行时从一种语言切换到另一种语言的速度——包括获取新翻译、重新渲染组件和更新 DOM。"

